snippet.title: Fate, God, Luck or Effort What Decides Your Success? | Sadhguru
snippet.description:
A seeker asks Sadhguru whether luck, fate and God decide our success. Sadhguru tells us that whether they play a role in being successful or not is not something we need to bother about. It is more important to focus on making an incisive effort.

To Watch this video in Tamil - https://youtu.be/SaaNVVjY1lI

#Sadhguru
Yogi, mystic and visionary, Sadhguru is a spiritual master with a difference. An arresting blend of profundity and pragmatism, his life and work serves as a reminder that yoga is a contemporary science, vitally relevant to our times.
